{
  "texts": [
    "• EKG improved safety compliance by 23.6% over ontology-based methods.",
    "• Framework demonstrated ≤1.8s average processing time across task categories.",
    "• Unified knowledge representation reduced safety violations by 81.3%.",
    "• Human evaluation results indicate high levels of usability, effectiveness, and safety, with mean scores of 4.2, 4.5, and 4.7, respectively.V.",
    "Our framework, which integrates Large Language Models (LLMs) and Embodied Knowledge Graphs (EKGs), holds promise for enhancing the safety of service robots."
  ]
}